{"tid":812433,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"龍蝦包食評 - Lobster Central","createTime":"2018-09-09T15:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T05:55:27.000Z","uid":175988,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3259a2bacac574d7accc73cecec097e9afc86748","tid":812433,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>Lobster Central @ 中環</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1DGAWf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1DGAWf0.jpg&h=73ab1f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Lobster Roll</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包身鬆軟唔黐牙，牛油香足，外層烘得夠熱同脆口<br />\n<br />\n蝦肉尚算結實唔鬆散，但煮得有啲過腍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整體調味唔夠，檸檬汁同沙律醬太少，突出唔到蝦肉嘅鮮甜<br />\n<br />\n龍蝦雪藏味唔重，但缺乏海水味，亦太乾無乜肉汁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 非常一般，唔試無損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"c3389dd7539f9761d7e972a7f27f2fc7d22deff0","tid":812433,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427019346154a3403e067ce491ad44bef27b939f","tid":812433,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b385f6c1ef7df91f2498b49f1d9bab8d739fa9ea","tid":812433,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c3389dd7539f9761d7e972a7f27f2fc7d22deff0","tid":812433,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:20:49.000Z","msg":"中環價，$138<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm